name: The Soul of Abyss
description:
After the Wanderers found the amulet (Hieropine) in the last chapter, They felt strange and immersive energy from the amulet. Hieropine choose Mvdra first to connect their souls and mind, it was a bright light that possessed Mvdra. You could never see the light again after that because dark will always muffle your eyes, very strong power. Mvdra transforming into the form that they didn't see before, an ultimate form and menacing soul,

The Soul of Abyss.

1080x1350 px
